WorkItem.Description:
Rawr 2.3.14, Alliance Moonkin, shoulder slot includes item #48783, "Runetotem's Mantle".  Armory doesn't know about this item.  Wowhead comments indicate this item was never added to the game, in fact it appears to be exactly the same as item #48187, "Runetotem's Mantle of Conquest" except that the latter is properly labelled as Horde-only.
Â 
"Runetotem's Mantle" should probably be removed from the default item cache.
